{"tid":2446874,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"＊電姆真係好正呀","createTime":"2021-03-14T19:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T17:03:43.000Z","uid":58038,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8923918f29b2ff8797a63a02cb57cf8501ccbaf","tid":2446874,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我本身好鐘意女僕，女僕服真係好好J，特別係低胸裝，對波唧晒出嚟，揸一揸短十年命都抵。 <br />\n上星期去親戚屋企食飯，當然要老套地寒暄一番啦。 <br />\n傾傾下燒到我嗰個疊。 <br />\n表姨：有咩興趣呀藍仔？ <br />\n我笑笑口，都未諗到點答，我阿媽就已經搶住講：個衰仔好鐘意女傭架，D公仔放到全屋都係。 <br />\n當下表姨全家人都目瞪口呆，就連本來喺廚房炒緊菜嘅菲律賓工人都忍唔住出廳擘大個口望住我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d993284e550864074ff5697eecec14ff6045f1cb","tid":2446874,"uid":60736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人就咪撚咁弱智啦"},{"pid":"b089242cf14d787be70401ba9b99747122f9e9eb","tid":2446874,"uid":58038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d993284e550864074ff5697eecec14ff6045f1cb","tid":2446874,"uid":60736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人就咪撚咁弱智啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:33.000Z","msg":"20210315 我愛電姆"},{"pid":"1abd426b2ac818b936223edfa2eb918d4e1aeb7d","tid":2446874,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:35.000Z","msg":"有是咁的9/10"},{"pid":"837400c2565a61aaf3d96f4f485d7bf21617489c","tid":2446874,"uid":60736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b089242cf14d787be70401ba9b99747122f9e9eb","tid":2446874,"uid":58038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d993284e550864074ff5697eecec14ff6045f1cb","tid":2446874,"uid":60736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:12.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人就咪撚咁弱智啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:11:33.000Z","msg":"20210315 我愛電姆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:12:25.000Z","msg":"chow post 9"},{"pid":"85369f